      ‚Üí‚Ä¶
    17‚Üí## Pull Request Conventions
    18‚Üí
    19‚Üí### Commits
    20‚Üí
    21‚ÜíWe use [Conventional Commits](https://www.conventionalcommits.org/en/v1.0.0/).
    22‚Üí
    23‚ÜíWhen opening a pull request please be sure that either the pull request title, or each commit in the pull request, has one of the following prefixes:
    24‚Üí
    25‚Üí - `feat`: For when introducing a new feature.  The result will be a new semver minor version of the package when it is next published.
    26‚Üí - `fix`: For bug fixes. The result will be a new semver patch version of the package when it is next published.
    27‚Üí - `docs`: For documentation updates.  The result will be a new semver patch version of the package when it is next published.
